export ROS_ROOT=$PREFIX && python -c "import rospkg;s = rospkg.RosPack();ret = s.get_path('rospack');print(ret)"
export ROS_ROOT=$PREFIX && python -c "import rospkg;s = rospkg.RosPack();ret = s.get_path('rospack');print(ret)"

name: ros-rospack
raw_meta_yaml:
package:
  name: ros-rospack
  version: 2.5.3

source:
  url: https://github.com/ros-gbp/rospack-release/archive/release/melodic/rospack/2.5.3-0.tar.gz
  fn: ros-rospack-2.5.3.tar.gz
  sha256: 0b9db7d9b7c20d8f36204d3bda08ef5cf41f3f8f7e009862102603b9daf65429
  patches:

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win]
  run_exports:
    - {{ pin_subpackage('ros-rospack', 'x.x') }}

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - cmake
    - make  # [unix]
  host:
    - ros-conda-mutex * melodic
    - ros-conda-base
    - python
    - catkin_pkg
    - pkg-config
    - boost-cpp
    - gtest
    - ros-cmake-modules
    - tinyxml2
    - ros-catkin
  run:
    - ros-conda-mutex * melodic
    - ros-conda-base
    - pkg-config
    - boost-cpp
    - rosdep
    - tinyxml2
    - ros-environment
    - python

test:
  requires:
    - rospkg
  commands:
    - export ROS_ROOT=$PREFIX && python -c "import rospkg;s = rospkg.RosPack();ret = s.get_path('rospack');print(ret)"

about:
  home: http://wiki.ros.org/rospack
  summary: |
    ROS Package Tool
  description: |
    ROS Package Tool
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: include/rospack/macros.h

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - wolfv
    - lesteve
    - seanyen
